From mcarlson at fhcrc.org  Sat May 28 02:20:55 2011
From: mcarlson at fhcrc.org (Marc Carlson)
Date: Fri, 27 May 2011 17:20:55 -0700
Subject: [Bioc-devel] interest in wikipathway annotation packages
In-Reply-To: <BANLkTim1HmEd87v0Om_0H2Fw=hnzYc_rcA@mail.gmail.com>
References: <BANLkTim1HmEd87v0Om_0H2Fw=hnzYc_rcA@mail.gmail.com>
